- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possible category as the paper discusses the efficiency of the decoding algorithms. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a possible category as the paper uses geometric concepts such as affine-invariance. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possible category as the paper involves studying the properties of polynomials and their degrees.
